mist-radio-messages-1 = Umm... So, the helicopter is delayed.. Problems, you know. We'll keep sending you supplies, just hold on a bit longer.
mist-radio-messages-2 = I'm sorry to inform you, the helicopter is delayed. You'll have to wait. Just a bit more.
mist-radio-messages-3 = This is starting to annoy me! The helicopter is delayed!
mist-radio-messages-4 = Guys, I know you're still out there. The pilot reported seeing you, but there's nothing we can do! NOTHING! You're not the only ones who need help!
mist-radio-messages-5 = Should we send a plane instead? There's a landing strip there, right... No... Just wait...
mist-radio-messages-6 = I haven't forgotten about you, but we've got problems up to our ears. Hang in there!
mist-radio-messages-7 = The military needed help, we're sending them over, and then we'll come for you right away!
mist-radio-messages-8 = The helicopter will come for you very soon... And show you a movie, oh for... where did it fly off to now!?
